{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/javascript/3","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"e1f36b88-3c3c-522a-adb8-78eb757b8e94","html":"<p>항상 그냥 미궁으로 남아있던 this를 오늘이 되어서야 처음 정리 해봅니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"자바스크립트-this에-대하여\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%90%EB%B0%94%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8-this%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%98%EC%97%AC\" aria-label=\"자바스크립트 this에 대하여 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>자바스크립트 this에 대하여</h3>\n<p>this는 Java에서는 자기자신 자체를 가리키는 객체이지만, 자바스크립트에서는 this에 해당하는 객체가 너무 다양합니다.</p>\n<p>다양하게 바뀌는 조건은 <strong>함수의 호출 방식 때문</strong>이라고 합니다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"함수-호출-방식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-%ED%98%B8%EC%B6%9C-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"함수 호출 방식 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>함수 호출 방식</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">foo</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 1. 함수 호출</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// window</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// window.foo();</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 2. 메소드 호출</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> foo<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> foo <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nobj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// obj</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 3. 생성자 함수 호출</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> instance <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// instance</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 4. apply/call/bind 호출</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bar\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// bar</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">apply</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// bar</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">bind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// bar</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"함수-호출\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-%ED%98%B8%EC%B6%9C\" aria-label=\"함수 호출 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>함수 호출</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>전역에서 this\n전역객체(Global Object)는 모든 객체의 유일한 최상위 객체를 의미하며 일반적으로 <u>Browser-side에서는 <strong>window</strong>, Server-side(Node.js)에서는 <strong>global</strong> 객체</u>를 의미합니다.</li>\n<li>기본적으로 this는 전역 객체에 바인딩 된다.</li>\n<li>\n<p>메소드의 내부함수의 경우도 this는 전역 객체에 바인딩</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\nvalue<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token function-variable function\">foo</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo's this: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// obj</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo's this.value: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 100</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">bar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar's this: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// window</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar's this.value: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">bar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nobj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>콜백함수의 경우에도 this는 전역객체에 바인딩된다. (예, setTimeout에서 콜백인자)</li>\n<li>\n<p>내부함수는 일반 함수, 메소드, 콜백함수 어디에서 선언되었든 관게없이 this는 전역객체를 바인딩한다. (아래 코드 예시는 this가 전역을 회피하는 방법)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\nvalue<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token function-variable function\">foo</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> that <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Workaround : this === obj</span>\n\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo's this: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// obj</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo's this.value: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 100</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">bar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar's this: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// window</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar's this.value: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1</span>\n\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar's that: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> that<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// obj</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar's that.value: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> that<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 100</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">bar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nobj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이렇게 회피하는 방법 이외에 명시적으로 바인딩하기위해 apply, call, bind가 존재 합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\nvalue<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token function-variable function\">foo</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo's this: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// obj</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo's this.value: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 100</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">bar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar's this: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// obj</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar's this.value: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 100</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bar's arguments: \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> arguments<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">bar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">apply</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">bar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">bar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">bind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nobj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이런식..이였군</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"메소드-호출\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A9%94%EC%86%8C%EB%93%9C-%ED%98%B8%EC%B6%9C\" aria-label=\"메소드 호출 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>메소드 호출</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>정의를 다른 객체에서 해도 해당 메소드를 호출한 객체에 바인딩된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> obj1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\nname<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Lee\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token function-variable function\">sayName</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> obj2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\nname<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Kim\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nobj2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sayName <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> obj1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sayName<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nobj1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sayName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Lee</span>\nobj2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sayName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Kim</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>프로토타입 객체도 메소드를 가지고 해당 메소드 내부에서의 this도 메소드를 호출한 객체에 바이 바인딩된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">getName</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> me <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Lee\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>me<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Lee</span>\n\n<span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Kim\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Kim</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"생성자-함수-호출\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%EC%9E%90-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-%ED%98%B8%EC%B6%9C\" aria-label=\"생성자 함수 호출 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>생성자 함수 호출</h4>\n<p>은 추후에..</p>\n<h4 id=\"apply-call-bind\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#apply-call-bind\" aria-label=\"apply call bind permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>apply, call, bind</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>this에 바인딩 될 객체를 명시적으로 정해주는 함수들입니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h5 id=\"형식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%98%95%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"형식 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>형식</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Person</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> foo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 각각의 메소드는 생성자함수 Person을 호출한다. 이때 this에 객체 foo를 바인딩한다.</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">apply</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// { name: 1 }</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// { name: 2 }</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">bind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// { name: 3 }</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>apply(<code class=\"language-text\">this에 바인딩할 객체</code>, [<code class=\"language-text\">인자값 리스트</code>])</li>\n<li>call(<code class=\"language-text\">this에 바인딩할 객체</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">인자1</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">인자2</code>,…)</li>\n<li>bind(<code class=\"language-text\">this에 바인딩할 객체</code>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>apply와 call은 위와 같이 작업이후 함수를 실행하는 것까지 바로 연결되며 bind는 this 바인딩만 이루어집니다.</p>\n<p>bind(<code class=\"language-text\">this 대체자</code>)()이런식으로 사용하면 apply와 call과 같은 기능이 됩니다.</p>\n<h5 id=\"대표적-사용-용도\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8C%80%ED%91%9C%EC%A0%81-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EC%9A%A9%EB%8F%84\" aria-label=\"대표적 사용 용도 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>대표적 사용 용도</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">convertArgsToArray</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> arr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> arguments<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">slice</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">convertArgsToArray</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Error</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Array에서 제공하는 메소드를 사용해 작업하고 싶었지만 arguments는 Array객체가 아닌 유사 Array입니다. 이럴 때 아래처럼 사용이 가능합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">convertArgsToArray</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arguments<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// arguments 객체를 배열로 변환</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// slice: 배열의 특정 부분에 대한 복사본을 생성한다.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> arr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">slice</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">apply</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arguments<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// arguments.slice</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// var arr = [].slice.apply(arguments);</span>\n\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">convertArgsToArray</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// [Arguments] { '0': 1, '1': 2, '2': 3 }</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// [ 1, 2, 3 ]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h5 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.zerocho.com/category/JavaScript/post/57433645a48729787807c3fd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ZeroCho</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://poiemaweb.com/js-this\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">poiemWeb</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><del>분량 조절 실패.. 기록이 좀 애매합니다.</del></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/javascript/3","tagSlugs":["/tag/javascript/","/tag/language/","/tag/this/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-08-08T01:00:00","description":"자바스크립트에서 this에 대해 알아봅니다.","tags":["javascript","language","this"],"title":"javascript this에 대하여","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/624cc4a835e68430a8beec01cef8ac6c/photo.jpg"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/javascript/3"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}